Former soldier John Young , 66 , and his new wife Elaine , 54 , were sat in the front room of their home in Oldham , Greater Manchester , when thugs began pelting his front window with stones .
Mr Young went and opened his front door to the attackers only to be struck in his left eye by another brick .
He suffered an open wound to his forehead and a serious injury to his eye .
Police say the attack .